-- Berkshire Specialty Insurance Unit Hires Zurich’s Spoon Rafkin
-- B y   M e g a n   H i c k e y
-- 2013-07-02T13:47:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-02/berkshire-specialty-insurance-unit-hires-zurich-s-spoon-rafkin.html
Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A) ’s specialty
insurance arm named Lori Spoon Rafkin as senior vice president
of customer & broker engagement.  Spoon Rafkin was previously the broker relationship leader
for North America at  Zurich Insurance Group AG (ZURN) , the unit of
Omaha, Nebraska-based Berkshire said today in a statement
distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
